google-drive-mcp-agent

This project is an independent, agent-agnostic Google Drive MCP server.
It is not an official Google, Gemini CLI, Anthropic, or OpenAI product.

This repository's own source code is licensed under Apache License 2.0 by the
repository owner.

Upstream source inspiration and compatibility reference:
https://github.com/gemini-cli-extensions/workspace

The referenced Google Workspace Extension for Gemini CLI is a separate upstream
project licensed under Apache License 2.0. Its license remains attached to that
upstream project and to any upstream code copied or derived from it. This
repository is intended as a new implementation focused on read-only Google
Drive tools for generic MCP clients.
